    a { color: #0a66c2; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    .meta { margin-top: 16px; padding: 12px; background: #eef5ff; border-left: 4px solid #0a66c2; border-radius: 8px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="wrap">
    <h1>GLA6 Theme Park</h1>
    <p>This temporary live page is published from the repository root so deployment is available while GitHub Actions billing restrictions are being resolved.</p>
    <p>Repository: <a href="https://github.com/ChampagneCODE3D/GLA6-Theme-Park">ChampagneCODE3D/GLA6-Theme-Park</a></p>
    <div class="meta">
      <strong>Status:</strong> Single-page fallback deployment active.<br />
      <strong>Next step:</strong> restore full workflow-based publish once account billing lock is cleared.
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
